{"title":"山谷静悄悄","authors":["冯金彦"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷静悄悄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风在肆虐的抢劫之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷里只丢下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几片破碎的云影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面包和水被暴风吃光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而帐篷被它撕开擦擦手丢进山涧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破碎的电台零件"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是为了避风钻进了石缝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤远方的讯号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在岩石上被摔成碎片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而快腿的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向最近的村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要走１０天的路程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８个人默默地伫立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流血的夕阳涂抹山顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语言这时是多余的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一片只生长岩石的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的耳朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都捕捉到了死神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐逼近的脚步声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而那份珍贵的考察资料"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝着心血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝着大山古老的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面有一百条路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十九条通向死亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后的一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该让资料走出去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的目光都这样说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有命令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有动员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁留下？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下意味着死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走是一条通往鲜花的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（可剩下的粮食和水——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死神签发的通行证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只允许一个人通行）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８双手臂　缓缓地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林般在山坡上举起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我留下……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我留下……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂的桅杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起的是死亡的篷帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来山坡上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开了七朵小花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野草也悄悄搭起了绿色的帐篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清明的雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常留恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而大山　则在岩石的家谱上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻上了他们的姓名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：辽宁省本溪市文联）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}